(1+r)
S = nT_0 + nT_0(1+r) + nT_0(1+r)^2+...+nT_0(1+r)^{M-1}
S(1+r) = nT_0(1+r) + nT_0(1+r)^2 + nT_0(1+r)^3+...+nT_0(1+r)^M
Sr = nT_0(1+r)^M - nT_0
\text{or }\quad S = nT_0\frac{(1+r)^M-1}{r}
