\displaystyle nT_0\frac{(1+r)^M-1}{r} = c
M
(1+r)^M = 1 + \frac{cr}{nT_0}
M \log(1+r) = \log(1 + \frac{cr}{nT_0})
\text{So }\quad M = \frac{\log(1 + \frac{cr}{nT_0})}{\log(1+r)}
